# The mesh-data parts under data_chunks/ are raw binary slices of .ply files.
# core.autocrlf must never touch them: any LF<->CRLF rewrite would corrupt the
# bytes and break reassembly. Mark them (and other binary assets) as binary so
# git applies no end-of-line or filter conversion.
data_chunks/** binary
*.ply binary
*.png binary
*.pdf binary
